name: Youth Media
tag_list: education, technology, health, mobile, student, young-people, communication
overview:
Youth Media is an established communications technology company which aims to bridge the gap between students and young people and educational and health institutions.

Based in London, UK, Youth Media work with a wide range of educational institutions providing direct desktop communications through their flagship software, EDD (Educational Done Differently).

Youth Media has worked extensively on the promotion of health issues among young people both through direct work with colleges and universities and through partnerships with the National Health Service, providing mobile technology to promote not only key health areas but also services and advice routes.
